# Docker build context = repo root (see apps/seamflow-api/Dockerfile).
# Keep the uploaded context small and force a clean install/build inside the
# image. Anything heavy or host-specific is excluded here.

# Dependencies — reinstalled in the image for the target platform
**/node_modules
.pnpm-store

# Build output — rebuilt in the image
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
apps/seamflow-web/.next

# Mobile app native + Expo artifacts (huge; irrelevant to the API)
apps/seamflow-app/android
apps/seamflow-app/ios
**/.expo
**/.expo-shared

# VCS / editor / OS
.git
.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
.vscode
.idea

# Logs & local env — secrets are injected via `fly secrets`, never baked in
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Misc
scratchpad
coverage
**/*.md
